Package: findpoolreg
Type: Package
Title: Find pooling region for precipitation extremes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Leandra Zanger
Maintainer: Leandra Zanger <Leandra.Zanger@hhu.de>
Description: This package provides a parametric bootstrap procedure that allows
    to test whether a set of locations is homogeneous w.r.t. their GEV
    distribution of precipitation extremes.
